[**Client SDKs**](https://www.covalenthq.com/docs/unified-api/sdk/?utm_source=arbitrum\&utm_medium=partner-docs) - official client libraries including TypeScript, Go and Python. TypeScript example:

   ```
   npm install @covalenthq/client-sdk
   ```

   or:

   ```
   yarn add @covalenthq/client-sdk
   ```

   ```
   import { CovalentClient } from "@covalenthq/client-sdk";

   (async () => {
   try {
       const client = new CovalentClient("YOUR_API_KEY");
       const transactions = client.TransactionService.getAllTransactionsForAddress("arbitrum-mainnet", "0xf977814e90da44bfa03b6295a0616a897441acec");

       for await (const tx of transactions) {
       console.log("tx", tx);
       }
   } catch (error) {
       console.log(error.message);
   }
   })();
   ```

